snippet.title: Daemon Detective Gaiden 2 - Trailer
snippet.description:
The official trailer of my new game! Daemon Detective Gaiden 2 is an action platformer game for Windows with around 20 hours of gameplay, local co-op and tons of secrets.

Interested? Check it out at: https://yaru.itch.io/daemon-detective-gaiden-2


Find my games (and gamedev resources too!) at: https://yaru.itch.io/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/GameDevYal
